                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            langAttribute="none"
                            text="&lt;p>Our culture of innovation and responsibility starts with our board of directors and extends out to every member of the company. Our board members work closely with AbbVie leaders to maintain our focus of putting patients first.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Robert A. Michael&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;AbbVie Inc.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;North Chicago, Illinois&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Roxanne S. Austin&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>President&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Austin Investment Advisors&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Newport Coast, California&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;b>William H.L. Burnside&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Retired Senior Vice President and Director&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;The Boston Consulting Group&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Los Angeles, California&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Jennifer L. Davis&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Chief Executive Officer, Health Care&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Procter &amp;amp; Gamble&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Cincinnati, Ohio&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;b>Thomas J. Falk&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa; &lt;/b>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Retired Chairman and Chief Executive Officer&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Kimberly-Clark Corporation&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Dallas, Texas&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;b>Thomas C. Freyman&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa; &lt;/b>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Retired Executive Vice President, Finance and Administration&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Abbott Laboratories&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Abbott Park, Illinois&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;b>Brett J. Hart&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>President&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;United Airlines Holdings, Inc.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Chicago, Illinois&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;b>Melody B. Meyer&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Retired President&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Chevron Asia Pacific Exploration and Production&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Houston, Texas&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Susan E. Quaggin, M.D.&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Irving S. Cutter Professor and Chair of Medicine&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Northwestern University Feinberg School of Medicine&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Chicago, Illinois&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;b>Edward J. Rapp&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Retired Group President for Resource Industries&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Caterpillar Inc.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Peoria, Illinois&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Rebecca B. Roberts&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Retired President&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Chevron Pipe Line Company&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Houston, Texas&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Frederick H. Waddell&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Former Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Northern Trust Corporation and The Northern Trust Company&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Chicago, Illinois&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
